title: War of the Roses: He Wants to Send Yellow Flowers?
description: Maggie has been hanging out with this guy and things were going great but now he doesn't seem to want to hang out as much and has barely been texting her back.  Is he seeing someone else or did something happen that caused him to lose interest?
